---
title: Crispy Falafel Salad with Pickled Red Onion, Cucumber, and Greek Yogurt Dressing
description: Ras el hanout infuses these falafel fritters with a unique North African flavor profile – one you may not be familiar with. Translating
literally to “head of the shop,” ras el hanout refers to the best spices at the market each day. Classic components include ginger,
cardamom, cinnamon, cumin, hot paprika, and peppercorns.
